UID:10391102-1774942200-1774953000@golatindance.com
SUMMARY:¡ECHALE!
DESCRIPTION:Echale is a Tuesday night COMMUNITY Latin dance event. The class which will vary from different dance styles and will take place at 7:30PM and the social will begin at 8:30PM. \n$15 for the class AND social. \n$10 for JUST the social. \nEchale is less about drawing tons of people to an event and more about drawing the right people. We are a social of all skill levels. Where the beginner won’t be intimidated to dance with the advanced. Where people meet up to have fun and be a part of the journey together. Where everyone knows your name. Where we stand for unity above all else. All of this may sound cliché (and cheesy)\, but we believe that in order to maintain a stable foundation of any kind\, it must be united. \nHence\, this is why we believe there is no strength without unity.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/echale-the-spot/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Rising Star\, 18505 Frederick Ave\, Gaithersburg\, 20879\, United States
CATEGORIES:Washington DC-Baltimore
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/610983561_122153686346913671_5474301483272526597_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Go Latin Dance
X-SOURCE-URL:https://golatindance.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260331T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T020000
DTSTAMP:20260331T231825
CREATED:20260209T224810Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260209T224810Z
UID:10444241-1774944000-1775008800@golatindance.com
SUMMARY:Get Together at the Lounge
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to the hottest new salsa and bachata social in DC. Each and every Tuesday\, let’s get together at the infamous Eighteenth Street Lounge’s new location and do what we love best: DANCE. Free salsa or bachata class starting at 8PM\, followed by social dancing with your favorite DJs from 9PM to 2AM. Drink specials. Bring your own food until 10PM. You don’t want to miss it!!! \nThe Eighteenth Street Lounge (ESL) steps away from the Convention Center metro station. The venue has it all: space\, floors\, amazing sound system…a legacy of respect for real music and musicians…and great vibes. \nIt’s about the music. It’s about community. It’s about connection. It’s about everything real and authentic. So bring the positive energy\, the good vibes\, and let’s get together.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/get-together-at-the-lounge/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Eighteenth Street Lounge\, 1230 9th St. NW\, Washington DC\, DC\, 20001\, United States
CATEGORIES:Washington DC-Baltimore
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Get-Together-Logo-Cropped.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Get Together Socials":MAILTO:get.together.socials@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
