SUMMARY:Bachata Corazon Tuesday Nights
DESCRIPTION:Shake off the workday with a night of pure Bachata and Salsa bliss!\nEvery Tuesday\, 6:15pm – 9pm\, we run Bachata classes for all levels of dancers\, from absolute beginners to advanced.\nFrom 9pm – midnight\, join us for an unforgettable evening at one of Melbourne’s most popular socials—our DJs drop all the hottest hits and dancers\, from all schools and interstate come together to share their love for social dancing. \nVisit https://corazon.events/tuesday for more details!
