SUMMARY:Bachata Tuesday Class & Social
DESCRIPTION:Bachata Tuesday Class & Social Every Last Tuesday of the Month\n\n\n🌟 Bachata Tuesday Class & Social Every Last Tuesday of the Month \nLooking for a fun way to spice up your Tuesday nights? Join us for Bachata Tuesday at Danzhaus Dance Center! Whether you’re looking to learn the basics\, perfect your moves\, or just have a great time dancing\, this event is perfect for everyone. \nEvent Details: \n🕖 Bachata Lesson (7-8pm) \nIntermediate Level Class with Bryon & Samm \nPerfect for those with some Bachata experience who want to take their skills to the next level. \n💃 Social Dancing (8-11pm) \nEnjoy a night of social dancing to the hottest Bachata hits\, with music by our resident DJ Thiencito. \nMeet new people and practice your moves in a relaxed\, friendly atmosphere. \nPricing: \nClass & Social: $25 \nSocial Only (no class): $10 \nLocation: Danzhaus Dance Center \n🌟 No partner required — Come alone or bring a friend! It’s a great opportunity to learn\, dance\, and connect with others. \nDon’t miss out on this fantastic night of Bachata! 💃🕺
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/bachata-tuesday-class-social/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Danzhaus Dance Center\, 1275 Connecticut Street\, San Francisco\, CA 94107\, San Francisco\, CA\, 94107\, US
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
END:VEVENT
