SUMMARY:Funky Mambo presents Salsa On2sdays
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Tuesday for exciting classes led by experienced teachers in a friendly\, inclusive environment. Feel the beat with top DJs\, dance at an amazing venue conveniently located just across from Tufnell Park tube station (Piccadilly Line\, just 2 stops from Camden Town). \nSalsa is the universal language of joy and connection—a skill for life! No experience needed\, just bring your passion.\n \nSee you on the dance floor on Tuesdays! Let’s make 2025 unforgettable!\n \n7.00 Door opens \n7.10 Foundation & Shines Classes \n8.00 Partner Work Classes \n9.00 Party/ Social Dancing till 11:30
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/funky-mambo-presents-salsa-on2sdays/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:FUNKY MAMBO\, 178 Junction Rd\, Tufnell Park\, London\, N19 5QQ\, GB
