SUMMARY:Todo Latino - Tuesdays with The Latin Collective
DESCRIPTION:London’s Legendary Latin Night is LEVELING UP!\nbrought to you by The Latin Collective\, Bachata Musketeers\, Cuban Collective \nWe’re thrilled to announce that our unmissable Tuesday Latin Nights are permanently moving to the spectacular SWAY BAR in Holborn – a 925-capacity venue with FOUR stunning rooms of dance! \nSay hello to the UK’s ONLY Weekly SBCZ Latin Superclub –\nSalsa | Bachata | Cuban \nSWAY BAR – 61-65 Great Queen St\, London WC2B 5BZ \nJust 5 mins from Holborn Tube \nFREE street parking nearby \nWhat’s On Every Tuesday: \n7:00–7:30PM – Free Intro Classes: Salsa\, Bachata\n7:30–9:30PM – Full Class Schedule (All Levels):\nCLASSES IN 3 ROOMS OF DANCE:\nROOM 1: Xbody Salsa On1 (3 levels)\nROOM 2: Bachata Fusion & Sensual (3 levels)\nROOM 3: Cuban Salsa (2 levels) \nVisit Sway Bar website for class prices. \nFrom 9:30PM – CLUB NIGHT BEGINS!\nDance ’til late across 3 rooms with the hottest Salsa\, Bachata\, Cuban\, Merengue & Reggaeton\, brought to you by DJD & guests. \nCLUB ENTRY:\nFREE before 8:30PM / £6 after \nPhoto ID required for entry
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/todo-latino-tuesdays-with-the-latin-collective/2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Sway Bar\, 61-65 Great Queen St\, London\, WC2B 5BZ\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/TODO-Latino-Sway-Bar-Banner.jpg
END:VEVENT
