DESCRIPTION:LATIN HEAT TUESDAYS + TACO TUESDAY DINE & DANCE with SPECIAL FOOD PROMO \nHere are all the details below: \nLatinDanceX.com presents\nWHAT: Latin Heat Tuesday + Taco Tuesday Dine & Dance\nWHEN: Weekly on Every Tuesday\nWHERE: The New Local Restaurante y Bar (10432 SE Kent-Kangley Rd\, Kent\, WA 98030)\nCOST: $10 Cover / Complimentary $0 cover for Currently Active* Group Class & Private Lesson Students\n*within the last 2 months\nAGES: All Ages\nDJs: DJ Juanchata & DJ Maracas\nMUSIC: Salsa\, Bachata\, Cumbia\, & Merengue\nSCHEDULE: 8 – 8:30PM Intro Class\n8:30 – 11PM Social Dancing & Practice\nSPECIAL FOOD PROMO: 4 Tacos for $10 (Unadvertised / Ask the server for the special) \n*** No dance partner required. Most folks come without a partner and we rotate students during the class so that you get to dance with a variety of partners.\n*** No experience necessary as we will teach you the fundamental skills necessary to start social dancing as quickly as possible. If you want to vastly improve your dancing skills quickly\, then consider taking some private lessons as we do have that available as well.\n*** If you want to be part of a growing community of Latin social dancers of South King County cities like Renton\, Auburn\, Kent and surrounding areas\, please join our Facebook group by searching for “South King County Salsa\, Bachata\, Cumbia\, & Merengue” and requesting to join.\nLet’s keep dancing for fitness\, fun\, and for friendship with our fellow dancers. We appreciate all of you who have a heart for dance.\nCheers\, \nThe Team at DJ J&M Dance Events – DJ Juanchata\, & DJ Maracas\, & Marietta\n**A DJ J&M Production**
